title: Latvia: Drone footage captures Latvia’s last Soviet nuclear base before demolition
description: Drone footage shot on Thursday captured the last Soviet military nuclear base in Latvia, outside of Gulbene, ahead of its demolition. Video ID: 20170209- 042 ...
